707A641"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_4.png", "id": "326946172620699", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_326946175954032_4895921826098113970_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-nmGF9xOGzEQ7kNvgHuWA2F&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCky6TfJ8LZIx6Y-xlyhILm99byhKdHohVf0pCj9mUpqQ&oe=6707C708"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Screenshot_1.png", "id": "667537957658372", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982512_667537960991705_1442117798375954928_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wUU4ZLOxujgQ7kNvgGizhhb&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCISEXxNQg1I3bZPpQMMZIQeS4tR1frH9IMzesakGLWnQ&oe=6707AC68"}, "display_name": "Bliss - Visual Breathing", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Bliss is a revolutionary new way to practice breathwork in virtual reality.\n\nOur body responds to our breathing. Bliss uses science-backed visual breathing aides to help you relax.\n\nMost people don't realize, but there are simple breathing exercises that can significantly improve your health.\n\nBreathing at a particular rate for extended periods of time can be difficult and boring though. So to make it a more enjoyable experience, we've created beautiful visuals that help guide you through \"Resonant Frequency Breathing\" exercises. We call this Visual Breathing.", "short_description": "Bliss is a revolutionary new way to practice breathwork in virtual reality.\n\nOur body responds to our breathing. Bliss uses science-backed visual breathing aides to help you relax.\n\nVisual breathing guides you to breathe at your resonant frequency, which extensive research has shown impacts many areas of your wellbeing."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://getbliss.app/terms", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://getbliss.app/terms", "publisher_name": "Rockwell Ventures", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://g